Test aggregate command without required --with argument

```console
$ rabbet aggregate tests/data/iris/iris.csv
? 1
Error: At least one aggregation operation must be specified with --with

```

Test aggregate command with --with flag but no value

```console
$ rabbet aggregate tests/data/iris/iris.csv --with
? 2
error: a value is required for '--with <WITH>' but none was supplied

For more information, try '--help'.

```

Test aggregate command with invalid aggregation specification format (missing equals sign)

```console
$ rabbet aggregate tests/data/iris/iris.csv --by Species --with PetalLength
? 1
Error: Invalid aggregation specification 'PetalLength'. Expected format: column=operation

```

Test aggregate command with multiple invalid specifications

```console
$ rabbet aggregate tests/data/iris/iris.csv --with col1,col2,col3
? 1
Error: Invalid aggregation specification 'col1'. Expected format: column=operation

```

